{"tid":2490880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"律政司上訴得直 17 歲仔刑毁改判入垃圾站","createTime":"2021-04-16T02:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T02:58:23.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ed92c912e2012d6abe5971dfb6c4a25633c09183","tid":2490880,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:37:54.000Z","msg":"一名17歲被控於2020年5月13日，在沙田新城市廣場一期喜茶，損壞2部收銀機的顯示屏及1部八達通處理器，價值共$15,200的資產。 <br />\n<br />\n被告在2020年12月7日在温紹明署理主任裁判官席前承認控罪，判處200小時社會服務令。律政司不服判刑過輕，遂向高等法院上訴庭申請刑期覆核，高等法院改判入更生中心。"},{"pid":"1039f46245f050229e13fe062886dea4fe061d1f","tid":2490880,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"bfd65d3d6cb9a5e333d01e87d51e67dbdbf78946","tid":2490880,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1039f46245f050229e13fe062886dea4fe061d1f","tid":2490880,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推<br />\n屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}